comments.body: We updated to Ruby 2.7 yesterday which brought with it an RDF minor version upgrade, which broke sorting RDF literals along with strings. There are two collections with titles that are `RDF::Literals`, so this is breaking (see #5004.) The fix is to just roll back the version of RDF for now and add a test to replicate.
I tried to replicate locally but was unable to
it's also not a problem on staging.
